{"tid":2032942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【銅鑼灣有暴徒向警察擲磚頭 至少4名傳媒聯絡隊人員受傷】","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T11:06:05.000Z","uid":107470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2352b4dda4734e12f1d6c56c68b5f469e75d9bfb","tid":2032942,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"下午約4時45分，警方在銅鑼灣鵝頸橋附近執法期間，有暴徒突然向現場警務人員投擲大量磚頭、硬物及不明液體，有人員頭盔被擊中損毀。事件中至少4名警方的傳媒聯絡隊人員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方譴責暴徒的惡行，任何人以暴力及傷害他人的方式去「爭取」訴求，都是超出法律容許的範圍。警方絕不姑息暴徒惡行，定必追究到底。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGR5HhJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGR5HhJ.jpg&h=0bac23b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c624ab17cbc8e9f0c09370edcb766e6f9903dad","tid":2032942,"uid":107470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"外國有冇警察會少少傷放上fb駁同情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2a246bf769ed5c995ff7f5adcdc3c7666de810","tid":2032942,"uid":46688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c624ab17cbc8e9f0c09370edcb766e6f9903dad","tid":2032942,"uid":107470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"外國有冇警察會少少傷放上fb駁同情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:47:19.000Z","msg":"畀外國人見到咁就post上網肯定笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2b3f4c61c2cf40dbf813a14b27b02ac0a8ca98","tid":2032942,"uid":187755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"香港黑警快d 自殺死， 浪費地球資源"},{"pid":"d6c1ad6a79ff8f73ee7357774bef5338018b51fb","tid":2032942,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"呀蛇，辛苦哂！<br />\n流咗咁多血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h